title: Small Wins Aren't Bullsh!t
itunes:title: Small Wins Aren't Bullsh!t
description:
If you are constantly thinking "I should...," "I have to...," or "I need to..." then listen to today's podcast.
 
Today we talk about how important your own inner self talk is when it comes to losing weight and reaching your goals. It's your job to be your own best cheerleader when it comes to the small wins. And today, I tell you why.
 
Get the Free Course here:
http://phit.click/freecourse
